{"schemaVersion":1,"source":"docfx-mref-page","file":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter.yml","symbols":[{"uid":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter","name":"ResultJsonConverter","fullName":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter","kind":"Class","namespace":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Common","assembly":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.Results","summary":"A custom JSON converter for BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.Result that writes a compact and client-safe JSON representation. Behavior: - Writes the following top-level properties: - isSuccess (boolean) - messages (array of strings) - errors (array of error objects) - For general errors, delegates to System.Text.Json.JsonSerializer using the error\u0027s type and the provided options. - For BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ExceptionError, emits a safe, flattened object and deliberately excludes the raw System.Exception instance to avoid unsupported types (e.g., MethodBase) and oversized/PII payloads. Notes: - Deserialization is not supported and will throw System.NotSupportedException. - This converter is intended for outbound API responses or logging, not for round-tripping back into domain models.","remarks":null,"syntax":{"content":"public sealed class ResultJsonConverter : JsonConverter","parameters":[],"returns":null},"parameters":[],"returns":null,"parent":"BridgingIT.DevKit.Common","children":["BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter.#ctor","BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter.Read(System.Text.Json.Utf8JsonReader@,System.Type,System.Text.Json.JsonSerializerOptions)","BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter.Write(System.Text.Json.Utf8JsonWriter,BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.Result,System.Text.Json.JsonSerializerOptions)"],"extensionMethods":["BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter.BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.LinqFluentExtensions.DoAsync\u0060\u00601(System.Func{BridgingIT.DevKit.Common.ResultJsonConverter,System.Threading.CancellationToken,System.Threading.Tasks.Task},System.Threading.CancellationT